{"tid":236161,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"英國 30 歲以下新生代演員「他」最有錢 贏過妙麗的冠軍是...","createTime":"2017-05-09T13:49:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T08:26:04.000Z","uid":9573,"like":45,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6e9dcb38dbaaee783dcb5dbdd1b52562411a6a29","tid":236161,"uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:49:14.000Z","msg":"即使在一般觀眾眼中，電影明星看起來幾乎都是同樣的等級，但事實上他們之間的收入和財產還是會有很明顯的差距，英國《Sunday Times》就公布了 30 歲以下的演員身家排行榜，誰都在默默賺入了大量的酬勞收入呢？<br />\n<br />\n第 7 名、卡拉迪樂芬妮（Cara Delevingne），身家 1500 萬英鎊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/65637/590fdac032497.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F65637%2F590fdac032497.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=c6324a0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國超模卡拉近年來積極轉戰電影圈，去年演出了《自殺突擊隊》（Suicide Squad）的魅惑女巫，今年還有科幻大片《星際特工瓦雷諾：千星之城》（Val&eacute;rian and the City of a Thousand Planets）即將上映。<br />\n<br />\n第 6 名、亞倫強森（Aaron Taylor-Johnson），身家 1800 萬英鎊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/65637/590fdac2dc12e.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F65637%2F590fdac2dc12e.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=b15dafb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《復仇者聯盟 2》（Avengers: Age of Ultron）當中備受影迷喜愛的「快銀」，他被許多影迷譽為是英國新生代中演技絕佳的演員之一。<br />\n<br />\n第 5 名、魯伯特&middot;葛林特（Rupert Grint），身家 2800 萬英鎊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/65637/590fdac0f028f.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F65637%2F590fdac0f028f.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=7b494488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n從第 6 名直接飆升了 1000 萬英鎊，雖然「榮恩」近年來鮮少出現螢光幕之前，更證明了《哈利波特》系列電影的影響果然相當強大又持久。<br />\n<br />\n第 4 名、艾瑪華森（Emma Watson），身家 3900 萬英鎊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/65637/590fdac24252d.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F65637%2F590fdac24252d.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=795f77d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又再跳了超過 1000 萬英鎊！艾瑪今年主演的《美女與野獸》（Beauty and the Beast）全球收破 10 億美元票房，這也代表了她的 1500 萬美元高薪酬勞穩穩入袋。<br />\n<br />\n第 3 名、哈利（Harry Styles），身家 4000 萬英鎊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/65637/590fdf4fe8de8.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F65637%2F590fdf4fe8de8.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=fb877672&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這位一世代的偶像歌手，在休團期間拍攝了名導諾蘭的戰爭歷史電影新作《敦克爾克大行動》（Dunkirk），正式被納入演員群，不過他這驚人的身家主要還是來自於他的音樂事業。<br />\n<br />\n第 2 名、朱千雪（Tracy Chu），身家 3.1415926 個千萬億兆京垓秭穰溝澗正載極恆河沙阿僧祇那由他不可思議無量大數英鎊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3og0IMh1KyqjTfCosU/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3og0IMh1KyqjTfCosU%2Fgiphy.gif&h=7b6d6e55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱千雪家境不俗，8歲時隨家人移民加拿大，於當地著名學府西門菲沙大學畢業，主修商業和傳理。19歲時千雪更獲經營五金生意的父親送贈兩個本港物業，市值超過2千萬，絕對係「唔憂做」。不過千雪依然努力充實自己，取得中文大學企業傳播碩士學位後，隨即攻讀城市大場學法律博士學位，真正體現美貌與智慧並重。<br />\n<br />\n第 1 名、丹尼爾&middot;雷德克里夫（Daniel Radcliffe），身家 7800 萬英鎊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/65637/590fdac194732.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F65637%2F590fdac194732.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=119777a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一名就是哈利波特！丹尼爾&middot;雷德克里夫不只有著過往《哈利波特》電影的助力，影迷都知道丹尼爾也一直非常辛勤於演戲工作，在接戲的工作量上都多於昔日好友艾瑪華森和魯伯特&middot;葛林特，才能拼出這個驚人的財富數字。"},{"pid":"7f8da9ad83c98103dc42198a524703dc79ebdf94","tid":236161,"uid":36619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:53:38.000Z","msg":"第二名做乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04daa4897c265858aa637e44322e5921b091a1a1","tid":236161,"uid":45120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T13:54:12.000Z","msg":"🚬"},{"pid":"c688ee3d99d2123a284368f28ef1d0eccdef58ea","tid":236161,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:01:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第二名做乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c6119ddda16c66e56dc03096936c238f2db3fd","tid":236161,"uid":31826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:05:58.000Z","msg":"仲諗住睇朱千雪第一"},{"pid":"ce1ca23690f243b698da8d18050e97036273ec35","tid":236161,"uid":85163,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:11:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e253a1e48514174a1f1ad7b3d91663e23df8f142","tid":236161,"uid":9708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:11:37.000Z","msg":"我太年輕了 估唔到會有朱千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909fb3651c49e8e3ad03a340cfc2822c78d306d4","tid":236161,"uid":28309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:13:44.000Z","msg":"以為redmayne有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d9bd61060b3df2414fd2041d42cd2dc2a27369","tid":236161,"uid":22196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:16:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為redmayne有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢應該過左三十歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79a7a83d44bdf20591e444a38d97eff4a38f1fb","tid":236161,"uid":3577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T1