c=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b1977575692aff4b7f1586d4d310e8cd3f60741","tid":236161,"uid":8999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:42:33.000Z","msg":"話時話榮恩到底而家搞緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb45f7aecdd5ae95ae31e4edb7c9dfae00e727c8","tid":236161,"uid":43880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:43:13.000Z","msg":"千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12156d4ba1a402df8aecb0fbdc20dbea3c7cf006","tid":236161,"uid":953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T14:48:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  哈利仔鳩下鳩下都有成八千野 身家<br />\n<br />\n一線果d 有錢到咩地步 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有錢過個作者<br />\n<br />\nbtw jk 羅琳唔知有幾多收入呢"},{"pid":"954f9e6b86bee3fbb8ab01c55dfeac54c7d64c77","tid":236161,"uid":45373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T15:02:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  哈利仔鳩下鳩下都有成八千野 身家<br />\n<br />\n一線果d 有錢到咩地步 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有錢過個作者<br />\n<br />\nbtw jk 羅琳唔知有幾多收入呢</blockquote><br />\n都唔鳩啦 記得佢有幾套戲有hehe scene <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4762ef4d4b6fa450404f4a1d235477bbffc8661","tid":236161,"uid":22389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T15:03:30.000Z","msg":"無睇名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab0bd8c66b30e20d3072df5a5ff6f1b42bd4038","tid":236161,"uid":107189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T15:05:24.000Z","msg":"CARA 本身就係有錢女二世祖<br />\n係英國同HOLLYWOOD 都唔知食幾多仔同女! <br />\n人生贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0a8f87e8724a3fd07021039ce78a8572f642d4","tid":236161,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T15:08:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  哈利仔鳩下鳩下都有成八千野 身家<br />\n<br />\n一線果d 有錢到咩地步 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有錢過個作者<br />\n<br />\nbtw jk 羅琳唔知有幾多收入呢</blockquote><br />\nJK早十年前已經過億喎"},{"pid":"07c0f8e4eb28a710194882323dbe1f1431b69606","tid":236161,"uid":22240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T15:12:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  哈利仔鳩下鳩下都有成八千野 身家<br />\n<br />\n一線果d 有錢到咩地步 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有錢過個作者<br />\n<br />\nbtw jk 羅琳唔知有幾多收入呢</blockquote><br />\n都唔鳩啦 記得佢有幾套戲有hehe scene <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nJk Rowling 好似係12英磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01%E5%8D%9A%E8%A9%95-%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/67002/%E8%AE%93%E5%85%A8%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%BF%83%E6%82%85%E8%AA%A0%E6%9C%8D%E7%9A%84%E5%AF%8C%E8%B1%AA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%25E5%258D%259A%25E8%25A9%2595-%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB%2F67002%2F%25E8%25AE%2593%25E5%2585%25A8%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%2595%258C%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%2582%2585%25E8%25AA%25A0%25E6%259C%258D%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25AF%258C%25E8%25B1%25AA&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7b%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=935e4c39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01%E5%8D%9A%E8%A9%95-%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/67002/%E8%AE%93%E5%85%A8%E